      "content": "that's a good start for the economic side. but for the debate i need to dig into the \"social order\" part you mentioned. can you expand on that? specifically, what were the arguments for why keeping different racial groups separate was seen as actually helpful for preserving culture or preventing social friction? i need some specific talking points that frame it as a way to maintain harmony rather than just looking at it through a modern lens.",
